device in a body cavity?

763
00:44:54,213 --> 00:44:55,083
You want to take a peek?

764
00:45:02,830 --> 00:45:03,918
My daughter's got one
just like that.

765
00:45:05,528 --> 00:45:06,704
You don't know
how to play along, Jimmy.

766
00:45:08,836 --> 00:45:09,576
Let me clue you in.

767
00:45:10,272 --> 00:45:11,621
You make my life difficult,

768
00:45:11,970 --> 00:45:13,580
