twice as difficult.

769
00:45:15,625 --> 00:45:17,802
Those papers, you read them
and you sign them.

770
00:45:18,672 --> 00:45:19,760
What are they?

771
00:45:20,152 --> 00:45:21,109
It's a contract between us.

772
00:45:23,416 --> 00:45:25,200
They say you won't try
to illicit any information

773
00:45:25,374 --> 00:45:28,421
