I came here
to take you back with me.

1116
01:11:30,155 --> 01:11:30,938
What about Mom?

1117
01:11:34,638 --> 01:11:35,769
I'm having kind of a rough time.

1118
01:11:37,249 --> 01:11:38,946
There's some people
making me fight to see you.

1119
01:11:42,254 --> 01:11:43,255
You're such a big girl.

1120
01:11:45,126 --> 01:11:46,737
There, there, it's all right.

1121
01:11:50,088 --> 01:11:52,395
I wish it could be like
it used to be.

1122
01:11:54,092 --> 01:11:55,180
JIMMY: I know.

1123
01:12:03,275 --> 01:12:04,015
Jimmy.

1124
01:12:05,146 --> 01:12:06,322
This is Kyle Gorman

1125
01:12:06,496 --> 01:12:07,540
