to prove a point.

1139
01:13:08,209 --> 01:13:09,385
You guys thought
you could beat me, huh?

1140
01:13:10,777 --> 01:13:11,996
-You're in way over your head.
-Yeah.

1141
01:13:12,475 --> 01:13:14,868
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

1142
01:13:20,221 --> 01:13:21,005
I want to crush him.

1143
01:13:22,485 --> 01:13:24,225
Gloves off. Just do it.

1144
01:13:26,314 --> 01:13:28,447
I'm sure the IRS can find
a "“T"” not crossed,

1145
01:13:28,621 --> 01:13:29,405
or an "“I"” not dotted?

