01:13:30,710 --> 01:13:31,842
He's no rocket scientist.

1147
01:13:33,757 --> 01:13:34,801
Come on, you guys.
Listen to yourselves.

1148
01:13:36,977 --> 01:13:38,065
We are a team.

1149
01:13:38,239 --> 01:13:39,806
We will work as a team.
Clear?

1150
01:13:50,164 --> 01:13:51,688
Don't you have a friend
that works in ATF?

1151
01:13:52,689 --> 01:13:53,994
Wouldn't it be a shame
if O'Meara got caught

1152
01:13:54,168 --> 01:13:55,256
serving an under-aged drinker.

1153
01:13:56,693 --> 01:13:57,824
He might lose his license.

