1156
01:14:04,614 --> 01:14:06,006
MAN: Give me another one.

1157
01:14:06,180 --> 01:14:07,834
I got circles under my eyes.
There you go.

1158
01:14:08,008 --> 01:14:09,836
Ah, you'll always be beautiful
to me.

1159
01:14:11,447 --> 01:14:12,360
-WOMAN: Thank you.
-Thanks.

