01:14:24,503 --> 01:14:25,983
Let me tell you something, Gina.

1165
01:14:26,157 --> 01:14:27,419
These guys can do this to me,
they can do it to you.

1166
01:14:27,985 --> 01:14:29,334
To any Joe Schmoe
on the street.

1167
01:14:29,508 --> 01:14:30,466
MAN: Excuse me.

1168
01:14:32,250 --> 01:14:34,208
Alcohol, Tobacco,
and Firearms, Mr. O'Meara.

1169
01:14:35,427 --> 01:14:36,559
We have a violation here.

1170
01:14:37,647 --> 01:14:38,778
Is there any place
we can talk.

1171
01:14:39,823 --> 01:14:41,346
Now this guy, Cox,
I'm taking you to see,

1172
01:14:42,260 --> 01:14:43,435
