Yeah? Send them in.

1179
01:15:00,060 --> 01:15:01,888
Come on here, Liz,
come in, sit down.

1180
01:15:03,194 --> 01:15:04,369
I read the newspaper piece.

1181
01:15:04,543 --> 01:15:06,110
I saw the segment on the TV.

1182
01:15:06,284 --> 01:15:07,677
but that's not why
I'll take your case, huh.

1183
01:15:09,069 --> 01:15:10,375
I believe you're right
in what you're doing.

1184
01:15:10,549 --> 01:15:12,246
I believe you got
a constitutional basis

1185
01:15:12,420 --> 01:15:14,031
to support your position.

1186
01:15:14,205 --> 01:15:16,686
And I believe you can win,
with you, it's emotional.

1187
01:15:17,251 --> 01:15:19,863
If I were in your shoes,
I'd feel exactly the same way.

1188
01:15:20,298 --> 01:15:22,169
I know where the chink
in Van Zandt's armor is.

1189
01:15:22,648 --> 01:15:24,520
You've got him and his policy
backed into a corner,

1190
01:15:24,694 --> 01:15:26,130
