will finish him off.

1191
01:15:26,913 --> 01:15:28,262
Yeah, we got
a lot of work to do.

1192
01:15:28,436 --> 01:15:29,220
So I hope you brought
your lunch.

1193
01:15:38,011 --> 01:15:39,447
You know,
you never answered me before.

1194
01:15:40,231 --> 01:15:42,538
-What?
-Why are you doing this for me?

1195
01:15:45,802 --> 01:15:46,933
I thought you knew.

1196
01:15:49,980 --> 01:15:51,416
I have a thing
for the good guys.

1197
01:15:56,726 --> 01:15:59,946
