I see a lot in you that I like,
you're beautiful.

1212
01:17:10,756 --> 01:17:13,324
You're courageous.

1213
01:17:14,368 --> 01:17:15,500
And I feel like
you're my friend.

1214
01:17:16,719 --> 01:17:17,850
But right now I'm so...

